# pyenv
#   For a library or package, you might want to ignore these files since the code is
#   intended to run in multiple environments; otherwise, check those in:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1255, pipenv should generally check in Pipfile.lock.
#   For libraries, you should not check in Pipfile.lock.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   According to poetry/poetry#944, poetry should generally check in poetry.lock.
#   For libraries, you should not check in poetry.lock.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   According to pdm-project/pdm#1035, pdm should generally check in pdm.lock.
#   For libraries, you should not check in pdm.lock.
# pdm.lock

